Stops attacking and recovers <@ba.vup>{value}</> DP over the skill duration. While this skill is active, Locks up to <@ba.vup>{max_target}</> nearby enemies.
Locked enemies have <@ba.vup>-{-move_speed:0%}</> Movement Speed, <@ba.vup>-{-def:0%}</> DEF, and lose <$ba.invisible>Invisibility</>

Enemies caught in the tornado receive <@ba.vup>{atk_scale:0%}</> ATK as <@ba.vup>Arts damage</> and are dragged towards the center <@ba.vup>slightly</> once every <@ba.vup>{interval}</> seconds. The target and nearby enemies are dragged towards this unit <@ba.vup>slightly</> after the skill duration
